<number box="[978,1062,1863,1888]" pageId="2" pageNumber="220" value="0.5" valueMax="0.6" valueMin="0.4">0.4–0.6</number>
× width of eye medially (lateral view). Clypeus weakly longitudinally convex, anterior border weakly emarginate, with narrow smooth rim. Labrum flat, anterior border straight. Malar space weakly developed. Length of flagellomere 
<number box="[1197,1211,1936,1960]" pageId="2" pageNumber="220" value="1.0">1</number>
<number box="[1218,1302,1936,1960]" pageId="2" pageNumber="220" value="2.0999999999999996" valueMax="2.3" valueMin="1.9">1.9–2.3</number>
